Preconditions:
The `mapping` array must not be null.
The `nums` array must not be null.
The `mapping` array must have at least one element.
The `nums` array must have at least one element.

Postconditions:
The `nums` array is sorted in non-decreasing order based on the mapped values of its elements.
The original order of elements in the `nums` array is preserved if two elements have the same mapped value.